23:
Whoa. You're training even at this 
hour?
27:
That's amazing. I didn't take you for 
the diligent type.
30:
To be honest, I just couldn't get to 
sleep.
32:
And we've had so many talented 
people join us lately, you know? 
I'm just doing what I can to keep up.
35:
Still, that's really admirable of you. 
Are you training to become a 
champion, like Light?
38:
A champion? Heh, I wouldn't go that 
far.
41:
I don't think Light's expecting anything
like that from me in any case.
43:
And to be honest, I don't think I'm 
champion stock, you know?
49:
I mean, just look at Light. Or Stella or 
Nimbus. Or even you yourself, Arisa. 
Everyone's got their own incredible 
talents and strengths.
51:
I only hope that one day I'll be 
somewhere close to their level, you 
know?
53:
It's a lot of work just to keep up with 
everyone else sometimes!
59:
You're doing more than plenty if you 
ask me.
61:
I always thought I'd be with Losaria 
forever, no matter what happened.
63:
But things turned out differently. 
And it was because I wasn't strong 
enough.
65:
I've since learned that sometimes it 
takes work to be with those you care 
for most.
67:
What do you think about training 
together?
69:
I know it's a bit late, but... I can't seem 
to relax either.
79:
Whoa, now that's some sharp 
shooting!
89:
I just wish I'd been stronger before. 
If I had, then maybe Losaria wouldn't 
have been taken away from me the 
way she was.
91:
I'd honestly almost forgotten about it 
since coming to this world.
94:
So thanks, Alk... for helping me 
remember what's truly important to 
me.
97:
Yeah.
We may have different reasons, but 
I guess our goals are the same.
101:
Hehe. Let's try our best to keep up with
everyone else.
105:
This Losaria must be someone REALLY 
amazing, though.
107:
Your bow skills are already impressive
enough, but she's supposed to be 
even better? I'd love to see that 
someday.
110:
Yeah, absolutely! I'm sure she'd love 
to meet all of you!
113:
Somehow I already know Stella would 
take a liking to her.
117:
Hehe... I can't wait for that day to 
come.
120:
I'm sure it'll come sooner than later. 
We'll do whatever we can to help, too!
128:
In the meantime, I'm going to keep 
getting stronger!
